M|Buil|The |you plan the loop in reverse (Learn-Measure-bd) but execute it forward (bd-Measure-Learn). Speed through the loop determines competitive advantage.
M|Reve|Ever|"What do we need to learn?" This reversal prevents the most common startup fl: building something nobody asked for.
M|The |tx|\| Step \| Question \| Output \|
M|The |tx|\|------\|----------\|--------\|
M|The |tx|\| 1. Learn \| What assumption must we validate? \| Clear hypothesis \|
M|The |tx|\| 2. Measure \| What metric proves or disproves it? \| sc/fl criteria \|
M|The |tx|\| 3. bd \| What is the minimum we must bd to get that metric? \| MVP specification \|
