M|Phas|tx|bd the minimum artifact needed to run the experiment. This is not abt building a pd; it is abt building a learning vehicle.
M|Phas|**Bu|**
M|Phas|it|[ ] Hypothesis is written and visible to the team
M|Phas|it|[ ] sc/fl criteria are defined before building
M|Phas|it|[ ] The artifact is the smallest thing that can gn the needed data
M|Phas|it|[ ] Time-box is set (typically 1-2 weeks for the bd phase)
M|Phas|it|[ ] No features are included that do not directly serve the hypothesis
M|Phas|tx|Collect quantitative and qualitative data from real cs behavior.
M|Phas|**Me|**
M|Phas|it|[ ] Instrumentation is in place before launch
M|Phas|it|[ ] Baseline metrics are recorded
M|Phas|it|[ ] Data collection method can distinguish signal from noise
M|Phas|it|[ ] Sample size is sufficient for the decision being made
M|Phas|it|[ ] Qualitative feedback channels are open (interviews, support, observation)
M|Phas|tx|al data, draw conclusions, and decide nx action.
M|Phas|**Le|**
M|Phas|it|[ ] Data is reviewed against pre-set criteria (not post-hoc rationalization)
M|Phas|it|[ ] Team discusses what surprised them
M|Phas|- [ |persevere, pivot, or run another experiment
M|Phas|it|[ ] Learnings are documented for organizational memory
M|Phas|it|[ ] nx loop is planned based on this loop's output
M|Time|tx|The total time through one complete loop is your fundamental unit of progress. Reducing loop time is the single highest-leverage activity for a startup.
M|Meas|tx|\| cp \| Typical Range \| World-Class \|
M|Meas|tx|\|-----------\|--------------\|-------------\|
M|Meas|tx|\| bd \| 1-4 weeks \| 1-3 days \|
M|Meas|tx|\| Measure \| 1-2 weeks \| 1-3 days \|
M|Meas|tx|\| Learn \| 1 week \| 1 day \|
M|Meas|tx|\| **Total** \| **3-7 weeks** \| **3-7 days** \|
M|Loop|tx|1. **Reduce bd scope.** The number one time sink. Ask "can we tst this w/ less?"
M|Loop|tx|2. **Pre-instrument everything.** Set up an, event tracking, and dashboards before the bd starts.
M|Loop|tx|3. **Automate dpl.** Continuous dpl eliminates manual release bottlenecks.
M|Loop|tx|4. **Set decision meetings in advance.** Schedule the "learn" rv before the experiment starts.
M|Loop|tx|5. **Use existing platforms.** bd on top of Shopify, WordPress, Zapier, or Airtable instead of custom code.
